Source.Name: python-sdl2
Source.Summary: PySDL2 is a wrapper around the SDL2 library.
Source.Description: PySDL2 is a wrapper around the SDL2 library and as such similar to the discontinued PySDL project. In contrast to PySDL, it has no licensing restrictions, nor does it rely on C code, but uses ctypes instead.
